  node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts,null,project,240,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null
close_reason: Refreshed Sentry expected handled CLI classifier for live 2026-06-11 handled CommandErrors PM-CLI-1N/1M/1F; contract test and live Sentry/telemetry gate now pass with critical=0 high=0.
